5.0 Payment of compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
Privatsikring's ordinary means of payment is by bank
transfer. Privatsikring therefore requires details of
the relevant bank and account number in order to be
able to pay compensation.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
